#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:1
msgid "Qwen 3.5 Usage"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:3
msgid ""
"Qwen 3.5 is Alibaba's latest generation LLM featuring a hybrid attention "
"architecture, advanced MoE with shared experts, and native multimodal "
"capabilities."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:5
msgid "Key architecture features:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:6
msgid ""
"**Hybrid Attention**: Gated Delta Networks (linear, O(n) complexity) "
"combined with full attention every 4th layer for high associative recall"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:7
msgid ""
"**MoE with Shared Experts**: Top-8 active out of 64 routed experts plus a "
"dedicated shared expert for universal features"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:8
msgid ""
"**Multimodal**: DeepStack Vision Transformer with Conv3d for native image "
"and video understanding"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:10
msgid "Launch Qwen 3.5 with SGLang"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:12
msgid "Dense Model"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:14
msgid "To serve `Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B` on 8 GPUs:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:16
msgid ""
"python3 -m sglang.launch_server \\\n"
"    --model-path Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B \\\n"
"    --tp 8 \\\n"
"    --trust-remote-code\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:23
msgid "AMD GPU (MI300X / MI325X / MI35X)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:25
msgid ""
"On AMD Instinct GPUs, use the `triton` attention backend. Both the full "
"attention layers and the Gated Delta Net (linear attention) layers use "
"Triton-based kernels on ROCm:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:27
msgid ""
"SGLANG_USE_AITER=1 python3 -m sglang.launch_server \\\n"
"    --model-path Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B \\\n"
"    --tp 8 \\\n"
"    --attention-backend triton \\\n"
"    --trust-remote-code\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:36
msgid ""
"Set `SGLANG_USE_AITER=1` to enable AMD's optimized aiter kernels for MoE and "
"GEMM operations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:39
msgid "Configuration Tips"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:41
msgid ""
"`--attention-backend`: Use `triton` on AMD GPUs for Qwen 3.5. The hybrid "
"attention architecture (Gated Delta Networks + full attention) works best "
"with the Triton backend on ROCm. The linear attention (GDN) layers always "
"use Triton kernels internally via the `GDNAttnBackend`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:42
msgid ""
"`--watchdog-timeout`: Increase to `1200` or higher for this large model, as "
"weight loading takes significant time."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:43
msgid ""
"`--model-loader-extra-config '{\"enable_multithread_load\": true}'`: Enables "
"parallel weight loading for faster startup."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:45
msgid "Reasoning and Tool Calling"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:47
msgid "Qwen 3.5 supports reasoning and tool calling via the Qwen3 parsers:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:49
msgid ""
"python3 -m sglang.launch_server \\\n"
"    --model-path Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B \\\n"
"    --tp 8 \\\n"
"    --trust-remote-code \\\n"
"    --reasoning-parser qwen3 \\\n"
"    --tool-call-parser qwen3_coder\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:58
msgid "Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:60
msgid "You can evaluate the model accuracy using `lm-eval`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../basic_usage/qwen3_5.md:62
msgid ""
"pip install lm-eval[api]\n"
"\n"
"lm_eval --model local-completions \\\n"
"    --model_args '{\"base_url\": \"http://localhost:8000/v1/completions\", "
"\"model\": \"Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B\", \"num_concurrent\": 256, "
"\"max_retries\": 10, \"max_gen_toks\": 2048}' \\\n"
"    --tasks gsm8k \\\n"
"    --batch_size auto \\\n"
"    --num_fewshot 5 \\\n"
"    --trust_remote_code\n"
msgstr ""

